<table>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<th>Registration Deadline</th>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>22 days before Election Day by mail and&nbsp;online.</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p>*Virginia has <a href="https://www.elections.virginia.gov/registration/same-day-voter-registration/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">same day registration</a> for 21 days through&nbsp;Election Day. An eligible voter can register to vote in-person and immediately vote with a provisional ballot in this timeframe.</p>

<p><em>Updated on November 12, 2024.</em></p>

